---------------------------***********BufferedReader Vs. Scanner*****************--------------------------------------

1. BufferedReader is synchronous                       Scanner is not synchronous
2. BufferedReader should be used with                  Scanner should avoided to use in Multiple threaded application
   Mutltiple threaded application
3. BufferedReader is fatser as it                      Scanner is little slower, As scanner does parsing of input data.
   Simply read seq. of chracter

Make sure to close try with resources while using BuffredReader and Scanner